Package grid

Grid package A package containing the necessary classes and methods to build a grid with obstacles and tuples with special costs, as well as providing classes to easily identify the position of an individual in the Grid, and calculating the cost of the path it has taken throughout his life

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IGrid
    IGrid.java - An interface outlining the minimum required methods to be provided by an the grid
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coordinates
    Used to represent the coordinates of a point from the specified map
    Edge
    Used to represent an adjacent Point of a specified Point
    Grid
    Used to map the points, with obstacles, tuples, initial and final points
    Obstacle
    Used to represent an obstacle point
    Point
    Used to represent a "free" point of the specified map
    Tuple
    Used to represent a high cost zone (tuple)

Package grid Description

Grid package A package containing the necessary classes and methods to build a grid with obstacles and tuples with special costs, as well as providing classes to easily identify the position of an individual in the Grid, and calculating the cost of the path it has taken throughout his life
See Also:
Simulator, Individual
